quoteText: If you choose to communicate suggestions for improvements to the Website, the Search Encrypt Application or the Services (collectively, "Feedback"), we shall own all right, title, and interest in and to the Feedback and we shall be entitled to use the Feedback without restriction.
title: If you offer suggestions to the service, they become the owner of the ideas that you give them
